text: Svend Skrydstrup (born 21 January 1940) is a Danish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman featherweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Danish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Denmark Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sønderborg Municipality
